Name: In The End
About the game: features: Your dropped into a map, given 2 guns to start with, which you must use to fight almost endless waves of the dead. Can you Survive? NEW MODE! Bots Team deathmatch! You and your AI Team VS Another AI Team! NEW Zombies Map! (Eastern Village) As you get higher in waves, you will notice zombies getting stronger , and the weapons you started with no longer have much affect against the dead, so its time to look for the mystery crate . The crate will give you a random weapon for a cost. Tips As you kill zombies, watch out for dropped perks, like instant kill, ammo, health packs, and a nuke, which kills all spawned zombies. Enjoy, Swizzgamess.
